  2. How do players' performance change over time?

Conclusions¶

Did defensive improvments help teams lose less games at home over the years?¶

Findings:

  1. Teams with most improvements defensively managed to loss less games on average at home Limitations:
  2. Lack of information on how these defensive attributes are measured.

How do players' performance change over time?¶

Findings:

  1. Players individual qualities diminish by age overall
  2. As players get over 30 the speed of deterioration increases
  3. Some attributes improve after age of 30
  4. Most of the improvements happen between the age of 10-20

Limitations:

  1. Lack of information on how these attributes are measured
